<h2> Notes </h2>

<p>
@HI{{@EM{{ndesuka}}}} can contain the speaker's surprise or suspicion or strong curiosity
and may therefore cause offence. It should be used with care.
</p>

<p>
@HI{{@EM{{ndesu}}}} is not used to state a simple fact.
</p>

